Introduction

Rowoon, born as Kim Seokwoo, in Ilsan South Korea, is the main vocalist and visual of the boy group SF9 under FNC Entertainment. He debuted as a member of SF9 on October 5, 2016 with the group's first single album "Feeling Sensation".

A year after his debut, he started appearing in television drama series such as as "School 2017" , "About Time", and "Where Stars Land". Over the years, he became one of the most popular actors of his generation and starred as main lead in dramas: "Extraordinary You", "She Would Never Know", "The King's Affection" and Tomorrow".
